SGBVHighlights.project: Protection and Assistance programme for Refugees and IDPs in Duhok-Iraq - IDPs - GBV Unit
SGBVHighlights.summary: Harikar/UNHCR GBV unit conducted diffrerent activities in April for Syrian and Non-Syrian refugees in camps and non-camp areas.GBV unit completed EMAP approcah during this month in Gawilan and Bardarash camps. Furthermore, completed women speak out approach in all refugee camps for women and in Duhok as well. It is worth to mentioend that, CLC-Gawilan conducted GBV core concept training for save the children staff in order to get more information on GBV and referral mechanism. Also, CLC-managers in all refugee camps continousley have attended an online CCM and Protection meeting and shared the updates of the projects. Assistant project manager for GBV  has attended an online GBV WG, GBVIMS, PSEA Duhok Tf and PSEA Iraq network meetings..
